    Microsatellite data from brook trout

    brook_trout_genos.Rd

    These are genotypes of 307 brook trout from a study by Ruzzante et al. in 2019. Each fish was typed at 33 microsatellite loci. Missing data are denoted by NAs. The columns are: Population, age_class, Sample_ID, Length, Age, Chrom, Locus, Pos, gene_copy, Allele.

    brook_trout_genos

    Format

    An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 20262 rows and 11 columns.
